        {
            "title": "全日收市︱午後曾跌 恒指收升71點報25321點 友邦滙控齊領漲 阿里巴巴拖後腿",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股先彈後回順，午後更一度倒跌，最後雖然力保不失，但升幅仍大縮水。兩大藍籌國際金融股仍領漲，阿里巴巴(09988)則拖大市後腿。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230810_FI_source-web_9988-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230810_FI_source-web_9988-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生指數今早高開334點後初段反覆向好，最高曾見25736點，將升幅擴大至487點或1.93%，補回昨天下挫的裂口後隨即回順，早市尚能維持升200點以上，午後升幅卻再度收窄，午市中段終於倒跌，最低見25236點，跌12點，稍作整固後動力略為提升，只是仍難回復早市景況。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指最後收報25321點，升71點或0.28%，較日中高位時升少逾八成半。恒生科技指數一直跑輸，午後初段已開始轉跌，收跌33點或0.69%，報4796點；國企指數也跌32點或0.38%，報8451點。主板成交3218.72億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15710219-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e6%9b%be%e8%b7%8c-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e6%94%b6%e5%8d%8771%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b125321%e9%bb%9e-%e5%8f%8b%e9%82%a6%e6%bb%99%e6%8e%a7%e9%bd%8a",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-5.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-05 16:24:55",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "A股向好  深股重上14000",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股全日報升，深股重上14000，滬股午後升幅略擴大，兩市合計成交23900.38億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-16.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-16.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指全日升26點或0.64%，報4108點，今早以4109點開市，升27點或0.67%，最低見4090，升8點或0.2%，兩會宣讀工作報告期間升幅擴大，全日最高見4125點，升43點或1.05%，全日成交10680.44億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指全日升171點或1.23%，報14088點，今早開市已重越14000點，開報14160點，升242點或1.74%，全日最高見14202，升285點或2.05%，為全日高位，午後收窄至13999，升82點或0.59%，全日成交13219.94億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數全日升45點或0.98%，報4647，今早開升49點或1.07%，開報4651點；</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">創業板指數全日報3216，升52點或1.66%，今早開市報3236點，升71點或2.27%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15709890-a%e8%82%a1%e5%90%91%e5%a5%bd-%e6%b7%b1%e8%82%a1%e9%87%8d%e4%b8%8a14000",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-14.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-05 15:14:55",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "日股午後升勢再緩 全日仍反彈1032點或1.9%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">亞洲主要股市午後升勢齊齊持續放緩，日股亦無例外。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/Financial_Markets_24198055000570.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/Financial_Markets_24198055000570.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">日經平均指數收市時升幅，由早市最多逾2000點，收窄至1032點或1.9%，收報55278點。計入今日反彈後，日股本周累計暫仍跌3572點或6.06%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">韓股在今日報復式反彈近10%後，本周累計暫時仍跌660點或10.57%。台股本周累計暫則跌1741點或4.92%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15709794-%e6%97%a5%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e5%8d%87%e5%8b%a2%e5%86%8d%e7%b7%a9-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e4%bb%8d%e5%8f%8d%e5%bd%881032%e9%bb%9e%e6%88%961-9",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250227_FI_source-ap_Japan_Financial_Markets-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-05 14:53:37",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "韓股全日報復式反彈9.63%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">韓股在昨天急跌逾12%後，今日出現報復式反彈，南韓首爾綜合指數最高曾衝上5715點，差不多完全收復昨天失地。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">指數升越5710點後卻未能再下一城，最後收報5583點，升幅收窄至490點或9.63%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">整周計算，韓指暫時仍跌660點或10.57%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15709767-%e9%9f%93%e8%82%a1%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e5%a0%b1%e5%be%a9%e5%bc%8f%e5%8f%8d%e5%bd%889-63",
